      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it represents a distinguished choice for the discerning driver seeking quality without compromise. Experience the assurance of a vehicle prepared to our exacting professional standards.",
